Text.Value: That... bloody... tiefling...
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*

EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW ANSWER - DELETE IF NOT NEEDED

Text.Value: *The corpse pauses, perhaps resisting the truth.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Who is Ramazith?
Leave.
How do I avoid the traps?
All magic... can be... dispelled...
How did you become the owner of this place?
How did you learn to imprison the Nightsong?
Lower floor... magic repository... vault key...
Any security measures I should be aware of in your repository?
Ramazith's notes... Balthazar's magic...
Who is more powerful, you or your apprentice?
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Ramazith... gone... Open for the taking...
Where do you store your valuables?
Where did Ramazith go?
Traps... spells... deathly to the touch...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Powerful mage... spell-maker...

Synopsis: Speak with Dead dialog with Lorroakan. He will give some information on his backstory, relationship
